Description: Build interactive HTML dashboards from R using a simple, 
    composable grammar. Create visualizations, organize them into pages, 
    and generate complete dashboards with navigation, theming, and 
    interactivity. Powered by Highcharts for charts and Quarto for 
    rendering.
